reviewText: Wonderful Love story. If you get the same set ( with this same picture) on box ,you should get the same quality as the one I purchased. In fact all 4 series are very good as far as quality and english subtitles. and of course the stories are beautiful. Lee San,wind of the Palace ( Part I ) 1 ~ 25 End
I loved this drama. The acting, costumes, and the plot are great.  It is very easy to be swept up in the storyline and the plight of the characters.  Every Korean drama fan should own this series.
